# System Admin Portal (§13.5, tier-0) — HQ-side configuration.

# Where this portal reaches a Centre Edge in dev (proxied under /api/*).
# In production the HQ WireGuard link carries this; never a public URL.
EDGE_URL=http://127.0.0.1:4000

# ── THE decryption key (HSM stand-in) ───────────────────────────────────
# RSA private key (PKCS8 PEM) matching the Edge's SYSTEM_ADMIN_PUBLIC_KEY_PEM.
# In production this key lives ONLY inside the HQ HSM and this variable does
# not exist — the unwrap is an HSM operation. For development, generate a
# pair with:  node scripts/gen-hq-keypair.mjs
# and paste the private half here (literal \n escapes are accepted).
HQ_PRIVATE_KEY_PEM=
